{
    "name": "Pale Stranger",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Pale strangers are wasted-looking undead that wear dry, dusty garb, usually a uniform or clothing with similar significance. They always carry one or more small arms, with many ancient pale strangers favoring the weapons of bygone eras.<br/><br/> A pale stranger arises from the corpse of a small arms expert who was killed through betrayal, was slain by a hated enemy, or died while seeking vengeance for an act committed against him or his family. The first act of an arisen pale stranger is to kill the person or entities responsible for his death."
        }
    ],
